{"id":624360,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/12/【立此存照】触目惊心：evil-man-中国男性之恶/","date":"2019-12-14T08:24:51Z","modified":"2019-12-14T08:24:51Z","title":"【立此存照】触目惊心：“Evil Man &#8211; 中国男性之恶”","content":"<p>12月14日，有网友将近几年来所有见诸媒体报道的针对中国女性的暴力、骚扰、性侵等事件总结于某github页面，取名为“Evil Man &#8211; 中国男性之恶”。</p>\n<p>页面地址：<a href=\"https://github.com/CNwoman-bot/evil-man/blob/master/README.md\">Evil Man &#8211; 中国男性之恶</a></p>\n<p>从这些罗列的数百条新闻事件中，我们甚至可以看到大量0-18岁的未成年女性受害者。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/截图.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-624366\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/截图.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"386\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/截图.png 1912w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/截图-300x211.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/截图-1024x719.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/截图-768x539.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/截图-1536x1078.png 1536w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/截图-1080x758.png 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>该事件总结甚至还按照事件类型如“高校性侵”、“网约车”、“恋爱伤害”等进行了细分。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/高校教授.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-624370\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/高校教授.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"513\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/高校教授.png 1422w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/高校教授-300x280.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/高校教授-1024x955.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/高校教授-768x716.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/高校教授-1080x1007.png 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a> <a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/恋爱.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-624371\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/恋爱.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"548\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/恋爱.png 1348w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/恋爱-300x300.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/恋爱-1024x1021.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/恋爱-150x150.png 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/恋爱-768x766.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/恋爱-1080x1077.png 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/恋爱-50x50.png 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a> <a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/网约车.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-624372\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/网约车.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"328\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/网约车.png 1512w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/网约车-300x179.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/网约车-1024x611.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/网约车-768x458.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/网约车-1080x644.png 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>事件标题均直链至了正式公开的媒体报道，来源有据：</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/的哥.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-624373\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/的哥.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"509\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/的哥.png 1418w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/的哥-300x278.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/的哥-1024x947.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/的哥-768x711.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/的哥-1080x999.png 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>即便这些事件是如此地触目惊心，但它仍然不是“完整版”，相信仍有大量的类似事件未被纳入统计，或者未受到媒体的公开报道。例如，有许多女性受害者或家属都是选择承受巨大压力在微博曝光事件后引起舆论关注，才推动了事件的后续处置。</p>\n<blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"TgthdPG3yj\"><p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2016/04/%e3%80%90%e7%bd%91%e7%bb%9c%e6%b0%91%e8%ae%ae%e3%80%91%e4%b8%80%e4%b8%aa%e5%8f%91%e5%be%ae%e5%8d%9a%e6%af%94%e6%8a%a5%e8%ad%a6%e7%ae%a1%e7%94%a8%e7%9a%84%e5%9b%bd%e5%ae%b6/\">【网络民议】一个发微博比报警管用的国家</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><iframe title=\"《【网络民议】一个发微博比报警管用的国家》—中国数字时代\" class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" style=\"position: absolute; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2016/04/%e3%80%90%e7%bd%91%e7%bb%9c%e6%b0%91%e8%ae%ae%e3%80%91%e4%b8%80%e4%b8%aa%e5%8f%91%e5%be%ae%e5%8d%9a%e6%af%94%e6%8a%a5%e8%ad%a6%e7%ae%a1%e7%94%a8%e7%9a%84%e5%9b%bd%e5%ae%b6/embed/#?secret=TgthdPG3yj\" data-secret=\"TgthdPG3yj\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe></p>\n<blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"YzrsouUqPQ\"><p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/06/%e3%80%90cdtv%e3%80%91%e4%b8%ad%e5%9b%bd%e4%b8%ba%e4%bd%95%e5%ae%89%e5%85%a8%e7%b3%bb%e5%88%97%ef%bc%9a%e5%a5%b3%e5%ad%a9%e6%b7%b1%e5%a4%9c%e9%81%ad%e7%94%b7%e5%ad%90%e6%ae%b4%e6%89%93%e6%89%92/\">【CDTV】中国为何安全系列：女孩深夜遭男子殴打扒衣拖行</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><iframe title=\"《【CDTV】中国为何安全系列：女孩深夜遭男子殴打扒衣拖行》—中国数字时代\" class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" style=\"position: absolute; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/06/%e3%80%90cdtv%e3%80%91%e4%b8%ad%e5%9b%bd%e4%b8%ba%e4%bd%95%e5%ae%89%e5%85%a8%e7%b3%bb%e5%88%97%ef%bc%9a%e5%a5%b3%e5%ad%a9%e6%b7%b1%e5%a4%9c%e9%81%ad%e7%94%b7%e5%ad%90%e6%ae%b4%e6%89%93%e6%89%92/embed/#?secret=YzrsouUqPQ\" data-secret=\"YzrsouUqPQ\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18271,38912,38984],"tags":[35407,10227,11494,26991,39502,11392,39501]}